Requirement Name: Termination & Resignation Initiation

User Stories Needed (IDs/titles): FF-018, OFF-019 As an Employee, I want to be able to request a Resignation request with reasoning. As an Employee, I want to be able to track my resignation request status.


Inputs Needed from Other Sub‑Systems: Employee Profile (Resignation Reason)

